<a href="/wiki/Economics_of_fascism" title="Economics of fascism">Fascist</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Georgism" title="Georgism">Georgist</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Islamic_economics" title="Islamic economics" class="mw-redirect">Islamic</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Laissez-faire" title="Laissez-faire">Laissez-faire</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Market_socialism" title="Market socialism">Market socialist</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mercantilism" title="Mercantilism">Mercantilist</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Protectionism" title="Protectionism">Protectionist</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Socialist_economics" title="Socialist economics">Socialist</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Syndicalism" title="Syndicalism">Syndicalist</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Third_Way_(centrism)" title="Third Way (centrism)">Third Way</a><br /></p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<div class="NavFrame" style="border-style: none; padding: 0px; text-align: center; border-left: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 0px;">
<div class="NavHead" style="border-style: none; padding: 0px; background:#ddddee; border-top: 1px solid #BEBEBE; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; height:1.9em;"><b><a href="/wiki/Economy" title="Economy">Other economies</a></b>&#160;</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="border-style: none; padding: 0px; background-color:transparent; font-size: 90%; text-align: center; display:none; border-top: 1px solid #BEBEBE;">
<p><a href="/wiki/Anglo-Saxon_economy" title="Anglo-Saxon economy">Anglo-Saxon</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Feudal" title="Feudal" class="mw-redirect">Feudal</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Global_economy" title="Global economy" class="mw-redirect">Global</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hunter-gatherer" title="Hunter-gatherer">Hunter-gatherer</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Newly_industrialized_country" title="Newly industrialized country">Newly industrialized country</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Palace_economy" title="Palace economy">Palace</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Plantation_economy" title="Plantation economy">Plantation</a><br />
